import {FloatingLabel, Form} from 'react-bootstrap'

export const FloatingLabelsDate = (props) => {

   let CurrentDate = moment(new Date()).format('YYYY-MM-DD')

   return <>


        <FloatingLabel
            controlId="floatingInput"
            label="Birthday date"
            className="mb-3"
        >

            <Form.Control
                required 
                type="date" 
                name="date"
                placeholder=" " 
                value = {props.val}
                onChange={props.handleChange}
            />

        </FloatingLabel>

    </>
}
